					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85018546" rend="visible">
						<summary>A recension of Sefer ha-gilgulim, with additional short pieces.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he"/>
						<msItem rend="">
							<locus from="1r" to="211v"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sefer ha-gilgulim</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">ספר הגלגולים</title>
							<author>
								<persName xml:lang="en" key="http://viaf.org/viaf/34704971">Vital, Ḥayyim ben Joseph, 1542-1620</persName>
								<persName xml:lang="he" key="http://viaf.org/viaf/34704971">ויטל, חיים בן יוסף</persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>See <ref target="Avivi_2008" type="page">708-710</ref>, vol. 2.</p>
								<p>Includes: a piece on metempsychosis, ascribed to Israel Sarug and transmitted by Menahem Azariah of Fano (folio 161v, headed ῾Inyane ha-gilgulim) and a commentary on Saba de-mishpatim concerning metempsychosis (folio 187r). Folios 190r-211v contain an  alphabethical index of gilgulim.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
